Package: precrec
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Accurate Precision-Recall and ROC Curves
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-08-04
Authors@R: c(
    person("Takaya", "Saito", email = "takaya.saito@ii.uib.no", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Marc", "Rehmsmeier", email = "marc.rehmsmeier@ii.uib.no", role = c("aut")))
Description: precrec is a package for calculating accuate Precision-Recall
    and ROC curves. precrec provides correct non-linear interpolation between
    two Precision-Recall plots. Calculated curves always maintain one-to-one
    relathiship between ROC and Precision-Recall spaces.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
